@host = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1) DB 원천 데이터 저장 + Redis refresh + 모든 pod local invalidate
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/db/product:100
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "value": "apple",
  "publishInvalidation": true
}

### 2) LOCAL_REDIS_DB: pod-1 첫 조회는 Local miss -> Redis hit
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/LOCAL_REDIS_DB/pods/pod-1/data/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3) LOCAL_REDIS_DB: pod-1 재조회는 Local hit
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/LOCAL_REDIS_DB/pods/pod-1/data/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4) pod-2는 별도 Local Cache라 첫 조회는 Local miss -> Redis hit
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/LOCAL_REDIS_DB/pods/pod-2/data/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 5) LOCAL_DB: Redis를 skip하고 DB fallback만 사용
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/LOCAL_DB/pods/pod-3/data/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 6) Redis-only seed
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/redis/banner:home
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "value": "spring-sale",
  "ttlSeconds": 30
}

### 7) LOCAL_REDIS: Redis hit 후 Local warm-up
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/LOCAL_REDIS/pods/pod-1/data/banner:home
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8) LOCAL_REDIS: DB에 있어도 Redis에 없으면 MISS
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/LOCAL_REDIS/pods/pod-1/data/product:not-in-redis
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 9) 정합성 실험: invalidation 없이 DB 업데이트하면 warmed pod가 stale local을 볼 수 있음
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/db/product:100
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "value": "apple-v2",
  "publishInvalidation": false
}

### 10) 수동 invalidation 전파
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/invalidate/product:100
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 11) pod별 local cache 통계
GET {{host}}/study/cachetier/pods/pod-1/stats
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 12) 특정 pod local cache 초기화
POST {{host}}/study/cachetier/pods/pod-1/local/clear
Accept: {{contentType}}
